data.description: Delightful open floor plan home in a great NW Lincoln City location. Enjoy the southern facing deck and the privacy of a dead-end road. 3 Bedrooms and 2 baths with the primary suite on its own side of the house. Spare bedrooms are ample size and share their own full bath. Large dining room. West side of 101, very close to the Connie Hansen Gardens as well as just moments to an easy beach access! 1 stall carport for parking and storage sheds. You won't want to miss this incredible opportunity to call Lincoln City home. Not in an HOA or park.
